OL,3,CTaliban introduces law banning women
OL,4,Cfrom speaking in public
OL,6,FThe Taliban are facing widespread
OL,7,Fcondemnation for introducing a set of
OL,8,Flaws which ban woman from speaking in
OL,9,Fpublic.
OL,11,FA set of morality laws were introduced
OL,12,Flast week to promote "virtuous"
OL,13,Fbehaviour, and included requirements
OL,14,Ffor women to conceal their faces,
OL,15,Fbodies and voices outside of the home.
OL,17,FRoza Otunbeya, head of Afghanistan's
OL,18,FUN mission, warned the new laws only
OL,19,Fadded to the "already intolerable
OL,20,Frestrictions" on the rights of women
OL,21,Fand girls.
