OL,6,FShe said: "After decades of war and in
OL,7,Fthe midst of a terrible humanitarian
OL,8,Fcrisis, the Afghan people deserve much
OL,9,Fbetter than being threatened or jailed
OL,10,Fif they happen to be late for prayers,
OL,11,Fglance at a member of the opposite sex
OL,12,Fwho is not a family member, or possess
OL,13,Fa photo of a loved one."
OL,15,FAfghan women living in the country and
OL,16,Facross the world have shared videos of
OL,17,Fthem singing in protest at the new
OL,18,Flaws.
