OL,3,CTaliban introduces law banning women
OL,4,Cfrom speaking in public
OL,6,FOne of them, a 23-year-old graduate
OL,7,Fwho gave her name as Efat, posted a
OL,8,Fvideo of her singing outdoors in
OL,9,FAfghanistan - and said she will not be
OL,10,Fsilenced.
OL,12,F"No command, system or man can close
OL,13,Fthe mouth of an Afghan woman," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"If you close one part of the body of
OL,17,Fan Afghan woman, another part will
OL,18,Fwork."
