OL,3,CTaliban introduces law banning women
OL,4,Cfrom speaking in public
OL,6,FEfat filmed the video in her home
OL,7,Fprovince of Badakhsan in the north-
OL,8,Feast of Afghanistan. She had
OL,9,Fpreviously protested against the full
OL,10,Fburqa and veil becoming mandatory.
OL,12,F"Because we are in Afghanistan, and
OL,13,Fthe region has less freedom and more
OL,14,Ffear, if a sound is heard, it will be
OL,15,Fshut down," Efat said.
OL,17,F"While I was singing, I had the same
OL,18,Ffear. That if someone heard it, it
OL,19,Fwould be the last time I sang."
