OL,6,F"There is obviously fear. But Afghan
OL,7,Fwomen carry the same fear in our lives
OL,8,Ffor the freedom of our voice," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe Taliban swept to power in
OL,12,FAfghanistan in 2021, following the
OL,13,Fwithdrawal of the military forces of
OL,14,Fsome Western countries, including the
OL,15,FUS and UK.
OL,17,FDespite an earlier pledge to honour
OL,18,Fwomen's rights in their governance,
OL,19,Fthe Taliban has faced condemnation for
OL,20,Fintroducing restrictive laws on
OL,21,Fwomen's freedoms.
